<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2026-01-23-dead-center.jpg" alt="https://archive.org/details/boris-a.-kordemsky-the-moscow-puzzles-1972/page/110/mode/2up" width="415" height="415" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-72622" srcset="https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2026-01-23-dead-center.jpg 415w, https://www.futilitycloset.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/2026-01-23-dead-center-300x300.jpg 300w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 415px) 100vw, 415px" /></p>
<p>In a shooting match, Andryusha, Volodya, and Borya each fired 6 shots, and each totaled 71 points.</p>
<p>Andryusha&#8217;s first 2 shots earned him 22 points, and Volodya&#8217;s first shot earned 3 points.</p>
<p>Who hit the bullseye?</p>

<div class='easySpoilerWrapper' style=''>
